message:
Add deck system UI and navigation reorganization

- Create DeckManager component for browsing/managing deck collections
- Integrate deck system API (10 endpoints: decks/voices CRUD + fork)
- Add loadVoicesFromDecks() to load voice configs from deck system
- Reorganize navigation: move deck UI to 'Decks' tab, Settings to gear icon
- Fix Vite bug: inline all TypeScript types in voiceApi.ts (types/ directory broken)
- Update Settings panel: add language toggle placeholder + About content
